    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add your <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and<strong> ground cumin</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 secs</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
