      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained beans</strong>,<strong> chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong>,<strong> chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3 min</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
