        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>tortillas</strong> to a plate</p><p>Put the plate in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 20 secs or until the tortillas are warmed through</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
