      "instruction": "<p>Garnish the <strong>bean chilli </strong>with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong>,<strong> grated cheese</strong>, <strong>chopped spring onion</strong> and<strong> </strong>a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Dollop over your<strong> natural yoghurt </strong>and serve the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
